00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:07,700
The Sawyer family

3
00:00:07,700 --> 00:00:13,940
Listen to the tape then answer this question.

4
00:00:13,940 --> 00:00:19,680
When do the children do their homework?

5
00:00:19,680 --> 00:00:24,060
The Sawyers live at 87 King Street.

6
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:31,170
In the morning, Mr. Sawyer goes to work and the children go to school.

7
00:00:31,170 --> 00:00:35,270
Their father takes them to school every day.

8
00:00:35,270 --> 00:00:38,960
Mrs. Sawyer stays at home every day.

9
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,960
She does the housework.

10
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:46,280
She always eats her lunch at noon.

11
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:51,430
In the afternoon, she usually sees her friends.

12
00:00:51,430 --> 00:00:54,940
They often drink tea together.

13
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:59,280
In the evening, the children come home from school.

14
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:02,450
They arrive home early.

15
00:01:02,450 --> 00:01:06,000
Mr. Sawyer comes home from work.

16
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:09,570
He arrives home late.

17
00:01:09,570 --> 00:01:14,310
At night, the children always do their homework.

18
00:01:14,310 --> 00:01:16,760
Then they go to bed.

19
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,760
Mr. Sawyer usually reads his newspaper, but sometimes he and his wife watch television.
